#
# Shorewall rules for urpm-ng P2P sharing
# Installed by urpm-ng-daemon — do not edit manually.
#
# TCP 9876: urpmd HTTP API (peer-to-peer media exchange)
# UDP 9878: urpmd LAN discovery (broadcast announce/listen)
#

# Inbound: allow peers to reach our daemon
ACCEPT  all     $FW     tcp     9876
ACCEPT  all     $FW     udp     9878

# Outbound: allow our daemon to contact peers and send broadcasts
ACCEPT  $FW     all     tcp     9876
ACCEPT  $FW     all     udp     9878
